com.camerontec.util.datamodel

Interface OrderedCollectionOfFieldGroups

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Nullable, OrderedCollection<FieldGroup>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Field
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NullField

    public interface OrderedCollectionOfFieldGroups
extends OrderedCollection<FieldGroup>
    This interface serves no other purpose than not being generic, which makes it possible for Java code produced by the expression compiler to be compiled by Janino. Once Janino has full support for generic types (which is not the case as per version 2.7.4), this interface can be deleted.
